          "entries": [
            {
              "title": "About the Course",
              "content": "Building on the habit of copywork in younger grades, high school students copy passages of any length that strike them from their readings into their commonplace book. For some students this becomes a lifelong keepsake and continuing habit.\n\nThis topic is included in the following course(s): Language Study: Grade 9, Language Study: Grade 10, Language Study: Grade 11, Language Study: Grade 12"
            }
          ]
